5度角向前推,大家明點做😁<br />\n<br />\n3.如果執到警槍,同佢地玩過遊戲,逐粒子彈唔小心跌落坑渠,洗手間,包保玩殘佢地...<br />\n<br />\n4.咁黑仔有狗用槍指你,可行情況試下用1秒用長竹,或雨傘打佢手同向上..<br />\n<br />\n5如果打狗,唔該搵手足集中打腳,上半身有盾牌你打係冇用,要傷腳同關節先有足,以上除左增強攻擊同防護能力之外,就係要令到狗驚,你要記住佢地都係人,唔係超人...<br />\n<br />\n6.哨兵必須去遠少少,手足唔好集足一個地方,必須快速移動,不停向唔同地方攻擊,切斷差人增援,攻擊完立即走人,玩殘班狗..<br />\n<br />\n7.盡量引班狗去橋下,用高空方式攻擊..<br />\n<br />\n最後10.1見,大家努力<br />\n一班CSD職員上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:09:09.000Z","msg":"有d用"},{"pid":"cc3655d4b7eabf5dbcb436ab001dd0fcd7591894","tid":1603293,"uid":43685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:42:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7a953f488492e1a8befbcbc4aa3b6aaf54e7141","tid":1603293,"uid":64138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:43:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c6bc843573db6e4e4c4b7d3d4209d6d3e5871ee9","tid":1603293,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:05:59.000Z","msg":"推上嚟等大家討論"},{"pid":"c2f90af69e8ce9d27005d4a4c22dd6a9ba969a26","tid":1603293,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:27:33.000Z","msg":"Useful information"},{"pid":"cc192efc10a094a6f3148d2aa0d2bdddc3d19b05","tid":1603293,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:28:29.000Z","msg":"拎到制空位 好有用"},{"pid":"90cf902493ebc01532e25ea9283f0413acb4f2eb","tid":1603293,"uid":48766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:29:50.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0de8f4202cfa245953b20ca33abd6ab6bac43312","tid":1603293,"uid":203174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:32:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a63c4bd477dd4b6997c0b607c2a792fed92f905","tid":1603293,"uid":197690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:41:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5a12c35db2d411cdce7501f683026b2b791362c","tid":1603293,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:41:57.000Z","msg":"